@chatBase = http://localhost:8003/api/v1
@authToken = user_token_123

### Listar mensajes (cursor pagination, newest first)
GET {{chatBase}}/chats/1/messages/
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Enviar mensaje de texto
POST {{chatBase}}/chats/1/messages/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "message": "¿Qué dice el documento sobre los plazos de entrega?"
}


### Enviar mensaje de voz (multipart/form-data)
# POST {{chatBase}}/chats/1/messages/
# Accept: application/json
# Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary
# Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
#
# --boundary
# Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="voice.webm"
# Content-Type: audio/webm
#
# < ./voice.webm
# --boundary--


### Eliminar un mensaje — responde 204
DELETE {{chatBase}}/chats/1/messages/55/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Borrar todo el historial del chat (soft-delete) — solo el creador
DELETE {{chatBase}}/chats/1/messages/clear/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Marcar chat como leído — responde 204
POST {{chatBase}}/chats/1/messages/read/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Listar mensajes pineados en el chat
GET {{chatBase}}/chats/1/messages/pinned/
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Pinear un mensaje — responde 201
POST {{chatBase}}/chats/1/messages/55/pin/
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Despinear un mensaje — responde 204
DELETE {{chatBase}}/chats/1/messages/55/pin/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Listar mensajes marcados como favoritos
GET {{chatBase}}/chats/1/messages/bookmarked/
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Agregar bookmark en un mensaje — responde 204
POST {{chatBase}}/chats/1/messages/55/bookmark/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Quitar bookmark de un mensaje — responde 204
DELETE {{chatBase}}/chats/1/messages/55/bookmark/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Listar respuestas del hilo de un mensaje
GET {{chatBase}}/chats/1/messages/55/thread/
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Agregar respuesta al hilo de un mensaje
POST {{chatBase}}/chats/1/messages/55/thread/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "message": "Interesante punto, ¿podés ampliar?"
}


### Enviar feedback (thumbs up) sobre un mensaje de IA
POST {{chatBase}}/chats/1/messages/55/feedback/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "value": 1
}


### Enviar feedback (thumbs down)
POST {{chatBase}}/chats/1/messages/55/feedback/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "value": -1
}


### Eliminar feedback — responde 204
DELETE {{chatBase}}/chats/1/messages/55/feedback/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
